Install SageMath
------------------

macOS:
Download and install SageMath 8.x binary (e.g., SageMath 8.1) from https://www.sagemath.org/download.html
Suggestion: pick binary with extension APP.DMG

Ubuntu: 
Suggestion: use built-in package manager
$ sudo apt install sagemath

Windows:
Download and install SageMath 8.x binary (e.g., SageMath 8.1) from https://www.sagemath.org/download.html

Launch SageMath Notebook
--------------------------------

macOS: Launch SageMath.
Ubuntu: $ sage -n jupyter
Windows: Launch SageMath Notebook.

Open the IPYNB file, and run the cell
----------------------------------------

Open "Ten-Year_Minimum_Errors.ipynb."
Click the play button.